desc: Columbus Ohio bakery + boutique for dogs. Fresh baked cookies, cupcakes and cakes for dogs. Featuring products from several women owned small businesses. Shop high end accessories, dehydrated treats and accessories for dogs.

layout.text: Celebrate with your dogs in style!

Human grade cakes, cupcakes and cookies baked fresh for your dogs to enjoy! Now featuring locally made accessories, and locally sourced raw/dehydrated treats. We support at least 7 small businesses! Stop in to shop selections.
